  "text": "The chromosomal location of THSD1 at 13q14.3 is similar to retinoblastoma 1 (RB1) gene region which has been reported with widely differing frequencies of allelic loss detected by LOH in CRC [CITATION_1] . This region is strongly associated with the progression of colorectal adenomas towards carcinomas [CITATION_2] .",
